Winners & Losers - Series 3, Episode 26




...Must Come to an End

As Bec says her final goodbyes and prepares to begin her new life, there's much cause for reminiscing. Jenny is a mixture of trepidation and excitement as she prepares to leave the Gross House for good. Sophie develops a crush on Sam's brother, Luke. As Sam gets excited for the wedding, a letter will turn her world upside down. Meanwhile, Frances throws herself back into her life as a career-driven woman but a shock discovery could change everything.




Original Air Date: 24-Jun-2014
